    <methods>
      <methodStep>
        <description>
          <section>
            <title>Grid generation</title>
            <para>The slope grid was generated using the previsouly created 30 meter DEM
                            (dem30_utm) in ArcInfo's grid function. Values in the grid were
                            converted from floating point to integer format and value attribute
                            table (.vat) was built. Although the original values are truncated, the
                            accuray is not significantly affected. Degree of slope is a value
                            between 0 and 90.</para>
          </section>
        </description>
